name: TAHI
description:
[PHYSICAL AVAILABLE TO FIRST COLLECTOR]

TAHI is Te Reo for 'One' - this is the first in a collection of framed mountainscapes, crafted by Hailtree in Aotearoa.

TAHI is approx 8x10" and framed in a black metal frame.

When the storms roll through the mountains surrounding my home in Wanaka, I always grabbed my camera, bundled up, and began to capture the magick flowing through the air. There's nothing like the air after a snowstorm. So crisp.

[Please contact me after purchase to arrange shipping this to you, shipping available worldwide]
